{"id_": "bf4d2d66-2d7b-4037-a571-9b2a5a88dabf", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"header_path": "/ANNEX F-2: MAJULAH PACKAGE/"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "40796cfa-e00e-44d7-a7a2-5fd4de70152c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f9680c491c54c9681f11bb6d26f8015c54847a13d6cc9608e524b11351b8a9db", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "c1d6fdaf-cd38-4d07-a915-f1f56479a1d2", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/"}, "hash": "cc2ad7613d062a19b5b8c252ff6447ef20cd20b8a14d6ec51982307b99565e04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "cc0a7014-8eb0-44b2-a8e4-c2259b2f7a40", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/ANNEX F-2: MAJULAH PACKAGE/(A) Earn and Save Bonus (“ESB”)/"}, "hash": "d90d666429397ed0b8542468dfeb5ff49937d245443288dddf2bc82e843a66eb", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "text": "## (A) Earn and Save Bonus (“ESB”)

Singaporeans born in 1973 or earlier will receive the ESB if they meet the following criteria:

1. Work and have an average monthly income of between $500 and $6,000;
2. Live in a residence with Annual Value (“AV”) of $25,000 and below; and
3. Own not more than one property.

Eligibility for the ESB will be assessed annually, based on income from the preceding Year of Assessment (employment and trade income) as well as AV and property ownership in the preceding year.

The ESB will be tiered by their average monthly income (see Table 1 below). The first annual ESB will be credited to their CPF Retirement Account (“RA”) or Special Account (“SA”) in March 2025.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 775, "end_char_idx": 1477, "text_template": "{metadata_str}

