", "class_name": "TextNode"}

{"id_": "2ad8b772-e68c-47cd-9b62-2df9dd83d721", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"header_path": "/ANNEX F-2: MAJULAH PACKAGE/"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "40796cfa-e00e-44d7-a7a2-5fd4de70152c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f9680c491c54c9681f11bb6d26f8015c54847a13d6cc9608e524b11351b8a9db", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "35fad43c-1625-4160-92dd-e7435cef2c50", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/ANNEX F-2: MAJULAH PACKAGE/(A) Earn and Save Bonus (“ESB”)/"}, "hash": "7bc50a0a62c935f37f6a217364e54a6ed312686c4b17fdf6dabdb3e9b6405643", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "165bac35-408a-44cc-8294-0ef113f5d944", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/ANNEX F-2: MAJULAH PACKAGE/MediSave Bonus (“MSB”)/"}, "hash": "9e7b9338a8e8528cd86fcc94ac37c81a8101706fc7a3466474277bd3d9477f88", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "text": "## MediSave Bonus (“MSB”)

All Singaporeans born in 1973 or earlier will receive the MSB.

The MSB will be tiered by their year of birth, the Annual Value (“AV”) of their residence, and whether they own more than one property as at 31 December 2023 (see Table 3 below), and will be credited to their CPF MediSave Account in December 2024.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3390, "end_char_idx": 3728, "text_template": "{metadata_str}

