{"id_": "3d835e3e-9cfe-4a0a-9bd9-5a4c2143d83c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"header_path": "/ANNEX B-2: ENTERPRISE SUPPORT PACKAGE/Budget Statement For Budget 2024/"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "3a0e3eb9-680e-41f6-9620-991849cfed92", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d787fcbb48f92cc638d2b8925eba4394a6ad0930b4a5fe147d1956ece90999be", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "e4ec4d67-ec5f-4bef-9465-ac6dff9a84bb", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/ANNEX B-2: ENTERPRISE SUPPORT PACKAGE/"}, "hash": "338d8a730882063e58824e48e1b2b247d7b98d019c2e99390c429a2939081d3a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "3e0b79cb-382b-4798-be27-c77c25d2044a", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/ANNEX B-2: ENTERPRISE SUPPORT PACKAGE/Budget Statement For Budget 2024/"}, "hash": "8f62565a15ec66087def2e06f6b66a6a2a6bb275939032567a704efc2f56d012", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "text": "### Support for Domestic Construction Projects
Support for domestic construction projects under the EFS – Project Loan will be extended till **31 March 2025**, with a maximum loan quantum of **$15 million**. This will support domestic construction firms amid a challenging operating environment.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2508, "end_char_idx": 2803, "text_template": "{metadata_str}

