{"id_": "fe10d6c8-af13-44d6-a94e-7f3a5a4753b1", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"header_path": "/"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "9a15a971-50a1-4e6d-90d0-7efdd6700471", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "6f469eaf38e2d273bfd28f30c9822731e4c19ecb873c63aecc5bb0cf8dec87bb", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "174db6f4-dfb5-45a6-af8a-c6a5c70ce873", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/ANNEX E-1: UPLIFTING LOWER-WAGE WORKERS/"}, "hash": "9c5d8d6ae52b3e94830f8b850b001488c3183fd3f50abd0faee8b60309598213", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "text": "# ANNEX E-1: UPLIFTING LOWER-WAGE WORKERS

Workfare and Progressive Wages are our key strategies to uplift our lower-wage workers. The Government will make the following adjustments:

- **(A)** Enhance the Workfare Income Supplement Scheme;
- **(B)** Raise the Local Qualifying Salary; and
- **(C)** Enhance the Progressive Wage Credit Scheme.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 343, "text_template": "{metadata_str}

