The gross monthly wage ceiling for PWCS co-funding will be increased from **$2,500** to **$3,000** in qualifying years 2025 and 2026 (see Table 1).", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 5188, "end_char_idx": 5404, "text_template": "{metadata_str}

