{"id_": "8e253254-3259-425c-9080-44514ae198ff", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"header_path": "/ANNEX B-1: ASSURANCE PACKAGE ENHANCEMENTS/Table 3: U-Save in FY2024/"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "510e8633-7372-4daf-b6f2-1ab563701af9", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "abf5bc444680b1d9a0bf9c4a44d8c91a64baa41ce56cfc2220994c4b50c76145", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "08454497-814c-4c27-946c-a4a1ff567bf6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/ANNEX B-1: ASSURANCE PACKAGE ENHANCEMENTS/"}, "hash": "7b36333f7a0d94f8644b8885b822fdab21e9b26fc66a554a96da10b86488c54f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "e7dd3ffc-bd9f-473e-af5a-9c28e5f63148", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/"}, "hash": "30250a771a35c334a733c7dadee96b20093a758d24dd6514e42e9ddda615439a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "text": "### Notes:
1. The B2024 COL U-Save includes the additional $20 of U-Save per quarter from the $1.1 billion COL Package announced in September 2023, to cushion the impact of higher utilities bills from increases in carbon tax and water price.
2. If the flat is partially rented out or not rented out, there must be at least one Singaporean owner or occupier in the household to be eligible for U-Save. If the entire HDB flat is rented out, there must be at least one Singaporean tenant.
3. Households whose members own more than one property are not eligible for U-Save.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4971, "end_char_idx": 5540, "text_template": "{metadata_str}

