{"id_": "df3c3862-e497-4f92-a2a0-85c4d5da3cd9", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"header_path": "/Budget Statement for Budget 2024/"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "510e8633-7372-4daf-b6f2-1ab563701af9", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "abf5bc444680b1d9a0bf9c4a44d8c91a64baa41ce56cfc2220994c4b50c76145", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "c28ef2f0-ab67-4a67-8127-af807ff87715", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/"}, "hash": "20f383882aa597272acaaefad2c9cc2b24e74f1dbfbec4e590d2e2622e429103", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "79dea1ff-5139-4fe1-8db4-4c3bdabf9fdc", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/Budget Statement for Budget 2024/Support for a Three-generation Family with Two Seniors and Two Young Children/"}, "hash": "19fdbaa0c29119dbc589d738cf53fe382a4aa438d6b90260b054b77a876136ad", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "text": "## Support for a Three-generation Family with Two Seniors and Two Young Children

In FY2024, a three-generation family with two seniors and two young children living in a 5-room HDB flat with a total monthly household income of $14,600 may receive support amounting to about $8,000 from the permanent GSTV scheme and the enhanced AP.

These benefits are in addition to what they may receive from other measures announced at B2024 (such as Majulah Package, MediSave Bonus, NS LifeSG Credits, and Personal Income Tax Rebate), and do not include subsidies which Singaporeans receive automatically when they access public goods and services, such as education, healthcare, and housing.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 10576, "end_char_idx": 11257, "text_template": "{metadata_str}

{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "
", "class_name": "TextNode"}

{"id_": "dca0fd16-a20d-42a1-909e-27c042c8ce36", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"header_path": "/Budget Statement for Budget 2024/"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "510e8633-7372-4daf-b6f2-1ab563701af9", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "abf5bc444680b1d9a0bf9c4a44d8c91a64baa41ce56cfc2220994c4b50c76145", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "7a42a0b8-dc6d-4b4c-aa7a-7901cae665a7", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/Budget Statement for Budget 2024/Support for a Three-generation Family with Two Seniors and Two Young Children/"}, "hash": "ab8350437377eb61591e46d0580d287dbace8ffa839143224c7900b779e8868b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "c6b84eaf-49f3-4a3b-ac44-438f796d6a57", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"header_path": "/Budget Statement for Budget 2024/Support for a Retired Elderly Couple/"}, "hash": "8d5a6d65fb06f95142d5538547ec5eb77cf115349483db0518afbc163eff1bb3", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "text": "## Support for a Retired Elderly Couple

In FY2024, a retired elderly couple living in a 3-room HDB flat with no income may receive support amounting to about $6,700 from the permanent GSTV scheme and the enhanced AP. These benefits are in addition to what they may receive from other measures announced at B2024 (such as the Majulah Package and NS LifeSG Credits) as well as schemes and subsidies to care for our seniors’ daily and healthcare needs in their silver years.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 12820, "end_char_idx": 13292, "text_template": "{metadata_str}

